Package: doi.gov
Title: API Client for doi.gov (Department of the Interior Natural Resources Revenue Data)
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for U.S. Department of the Interior natural resources
    revenue data from revenuedata.doi.gov. Provides access to revenue, production,
    disbursements, federal sales, and revenue-by-company datasets. All functions return tibbles.
